videos.description: Ed Morrow receives the inbound pass and rises up to throw down a dunk on two defenders.
videos.headline: Morrow throws down over two defenders

videos.description: Ed Morrow corrals the missed shot and throws down a powerful one-handed putback jam.
videos.headline: Morrow throws down putback dunk

videos.description: A foul leads to big drama between Myles Powell and Theo John which leads to John and Sacar Anim being ejected for Marquetet, and Sandro Mamukelashvili for Seton Hall.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Big drama leads to multiple ejections at MSG) 2019/03/15 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Big drama leads to multiple ejections at MSG

videos.description: Myles Powell lofts up a lob pass to Romaro Gill who slams down the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Powell connects with Gill for alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Markus Howard tries to hit the game-winning 3-pointer but his shot comes up short causing Marquette to lose to Seton Hall 81-79.
videos.headline: Howard misses pull-up game-winner from deep
